---
description: Admin and operations guidance
globs:
  - "src/app/(protected)/admin/**"
  - "src/features/admin/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Admin scope is moderation, disputes, refunds, supply controls, and marketplace operations.
- Favor operator clarity, explicit state, and auditability over decorative complexity.
- Keep admin-only logic in `src/features/admin`.
